<ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/InsaneClownPosse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/InsaneClownPosse">Insane Clown Posse</a> often reference Ninjas in their songs, particularly in the song "Ninja". <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Juggalo" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Juggalo">Juggalos</a> also refer to themselves as "Ninja".
<div class="indent"><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/Twiztid" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/Twiztid">What up, ninja?</a>
</div></li><li> Ninjas are among the many <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UnusuallyUninterestingSight" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/UnusuallyUninterestingSight">Unusually Uninteresting Sights</a> in Bonnie Tyler's "<a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/TotalEclipseOfTheHeart" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Music/TotalEclipseOfTheHeart">Total Eclipse Of The Heart</a>" video, which is set in a British boarding school.
</li></ul></div>
