<h2 class="bold font-l">Rioichi Cooper</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Rioichi Cooper is one of Sly's more famous ancestor, a Japanese raccoon dog responsible for the Ninja Spire Jump. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="0j44kt" data-video-descrip="Greninja is a water/dark-type Pokemon that can create shuriken-like constructs out of water." data-video-title="Greninja" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/0j44kt_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/0j44kt.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/NINJA" data-video-tropename="Ninja" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SuperSmashBrosForNintendo3DSAndWiiU" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/0j44kt.jpg">
